<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<XtraReportsLayoutSerializer SerializerVersion="17.1.4.0" Ref="1" ControlType="DevExpress.XtraReports.UI.XtraReport, DevExpress.XtraReports.v17.1, Version=17.1.4.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b88d1754d700e49a" Name="XtraReport" ScriptsSource="using System.Data;
using System.Drawing.Printing;
using Rowa.SmartDose.ReportRenderer.Interface.Sdmc;

private System.Globalization.CultureInfo _originalCulture = System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CurrentCulture;

private void XtraReport_BeforePrint(object sender, System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs e) 
{
	//Set Manually the Culture to german
	var currentCulture = System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CreateSpecificCulture("de-DE");
    	System.Threading.Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentUICulture = currentCulture;
    	System.Threading.Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentCulture = currentCulture;
	
	//Set the matching Text for the intake time
	
	DateTime intaketime = (System.DateTime)GetCurrentColumnValue("IntakeDateTime");

	//lblIntakeTime.Text ="Bedtime";

	if (intaketime.Hour==8 && intaketime.Minute == 0 && intaketime.Second == 0)
	{
		lblIntakeTime.Text ="morgens";	
	}
	else if (intaketime.Hour==12 && intaketime.Minute == 0 && intaketime.Second == 0)
	{
		lblIntakeTime.Text="mittags";
	}
	else if (intaketime.Hour==18 && intaketime.Minute == 0 && intaketime.Second == 0)
	{
		lblIntakeTime.Text ="abends";
	}
	else if (intaketime.Hour==22 && intaketime.Minute == 0 && intaketime.Second == 0)
	{
		lblIntakeTime.Text ="nachts";
	}
	else
	{
		lblIntakeTime.Text = intaketime.ToShortTimeString();
	}

	

/*	

	//Set pouchcounter visible / not visible
	int pouchCountIntakeTimeTotal = (int)GetCurrentColumnValue("PouchCountIntakeTimeTotal");
	int pouchCountIntakeTimeCurrent = (int)GetCurrentColumnValue("PouchCountIntakeTimeCurrent");

			
	if (pouchCountIntakeTimeTotal > 1)
	{
		lblPouchCountIntakeTime.Text = pouchCountIntakeTimeCurrent.ToString()+" / "+pouchCountIntakeTimeTotal.ToString();
	}
*/

}

private void lblMedicineDescription_BeforePrint(object sender, System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs e) 
{
	var data = (IMedicineData)DetailReport.GetCurrentRow();
 	var details = (IMedicineDataDetails)data.MedicineDataDetails;
	
	string tmpDetail ="";
	string formType = details.FormType;
	string color = details.Color;
	
	lblMedicineDescription.Text="";

	if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(formType) && string.IsNullOrEmpty(color))	
	{
		lblMedicineDescription.Text +=string.Format("({0})",formType);
	}
	else if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(formType) && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(color))
	{
		lblMedicineDescription.Text +=string.Format("({0})",color);

	}
	else if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(formType) && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(color))
	{
		lblMedicineDescription.Text +=string.Format("({0}, {1})", color, formType);
	}
}

private void lblLot_BeforePrint(object sender, System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs e) 
{
	var lotConc = String.Empty;
	var data = (IMedicineData)DetailReport.GetCurrentRow();
	var expiryDateMin = System.DateTime.MaxValue;

	var lotData = data.LotInfos;

	foreach(var lot in lotData)
	{
		lotConc +=lot.LotNumber;
		lotConc +=",";

		if (lot.ExpiryDate<expiryDateMin)
		{
			expiryDateMin = lot.ExpiryDate;
		}			
	}

	if (lotConc !=String.Empty)
	{
		if (lotConc.EndsWith(",")) lotConc = lotConc.Remove(lotConc.Length - 1, 1);
	}
	
	if (expiryDateMin!=System.DateTime.MaxValue) 
	{ 
		lblExpiryDate.Text = expiryDateMin.ToString("dd.MM.yyyy");
	}

	lblLot.Text=lotConc ;
}


private string ConvertDecimalToFraction(double amount)
{
	string result;
	bool hasDecimalPart = !(amount-System.Math.Truncate(amount) == 0);	
	
	if (hasDecimalPart)
      {
      	string wholePart = string.Empty;
                string fractionPart = string.Empty;

                if (true)
                {
                    int whole = (int)amount;
                    double decimals = (whole > 0) ? amount% whole : amount;

                    if (whole > 0)
                    {
                        wholePart = whole.ToString()+" ";
                    }

                    if (decimals == 0.25)
                    {
                        fractionPart = "1/4";
                    }
                    else if (decimals >= 0.3 && decimals < 0.5)
                    {
                        fractionPart = "1/3";
                    }
                    else if (decimals == 0.5)
                    {
                        fractionPart = "1/2";
                    }
                    else if (decimals >= 0.60 && decimals <= 0.7)
                    {
                        fractionPart = "2/3";
                    }
                    else if (decimals == 0.75)
                    {
                        fractionPart = "3/4";
                    }
                }

                if (fractionPart == string.Empty)
                {
                    result = amount.ToString("0.00").TrimEnd('0');
                }
                else
                {
                    result = wholePart + fractionPart;
                }
		
            }
            else
            {
                result = amount.ToString("#");
            }
	return result;

}

}
